title: GBA ROMS - Baldurs Gate Dark Alliance
description:
The ROM File for Baldur's Gate Dark Alliance (GBA)



    * Emulator NOT INCLUDED *




The only GBA game from the Baldur's Gate series, this game allows the user to choose from 3 classes at the start of the game. Travel through the 3 main areas, defeating monsters, gaining power and fame as you do. Equip yourself with the best weapons from shopkeepers and accept quests along the way. End the curse of Baldur's Gate once and for all.
